channel.title: Ok wth ip problem?
channel.description:

i go to whatismyip.com and it says the ip that i originally know of that i used. so then just to make sure i use the command box and type in ipconfig and my ip is totally different... i know it wouldnt be the safest idea to use my actual ip so im just going to use cross it all out and put an example of what im talking about..

SO THERE IT IS
